      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白，ActuatorController作为第一列的标题。那这一列下面需要放什么任务卡片？是具体的子模块吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，第一列下面放TelemetryStream和PLC Logic。TelemetryStream负责采集振动、温度这些实时数据，PLC Logic处理本地的控制逻辑。这两个都是ActuatorController直接管理的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "t industrial telemetrystream",
        "t industrial plc logic",
        "task1",
        "task2",
        "column1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，第一列结构已经搭建好了：IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController下面挂着TelemetryStream和PLC Logic两张卡片。接下来第二列是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column1",
        "task1",
        "task2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第二列应该是MQTT Broker，作为数据汇聚和转发的中间层。现场采集的数据通过MQTT协议先到这里，然后再分发出去。",
      "elements_involved": [
