    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "第二列完成：MQTT Broker作为列标题，下面有一张TelemetryStream任务卡。现在第三列怎么安排？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column2",
        "task3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第三列我想再放一个MQTT Broker，代表云端或边缘侧的代理节点。最后一张卡片放ActuatorController，表示控制指令最终回到执行层形成闭环。",
