    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "稍等，第三列的标题也是MQTT Broker，但卡片是ActuatorController？这和第一列的结构不太一样，第一列是ActuatorController标题配子任务，第三列是MQTT Broker标题配ActuatorController卡片？",
